= Robotrek (SNES) - Recipes =

This page documents the combination recipes in Robotrek (USA version).

'''Data Status:''' Verified from ROM at $01c200 (512 bytes).

'''Source:''' [https://github.com/TheAnsarya/GameInfo GameInfo extracted data]

== Overview ==

The combination system allows players to combine two identical items to create upgraded versions. This is separate from the invention system, which creates items from materials.

